text: Weilheim in Oberbayern (English: 'Weilheim in Upper Bavaria') is a town in Germany, the capital of Weilheim-Schongau in the south of Bavaria. ==Twin towns and cities== Weilheim in Oberbayern is twinned with: * Narbonne, France *Yelabuga, Tatarstan, Russian Federation ==References== Category:Weilheim- Schongau
title: Weilheim in Oberbayern
